@startuml
title UML state machine diagram

[*] --> ServiceCenterRegistration
ServiceCenterRegistration : exit / Account registered --> [*]

ServiceCenterRegistration --> ServiceCenterVerification
ServiceCenterVerification : exit / Login Service center --> [*]

ServiceCenterVerification --> ServiceCenterLogin
ServiceCenterLogin : exit / Logged In Successfully --> ServiceCenterHome

ServiceCenterHome : exit / Enter Damaged parts list --> Entering Damaged parts list
EnteringDamagedPartsList : exit / Return to service center home page --> ServiceCenterHome

ServiceCenterHome : exit / Expiry Notification page --> ExpiryNotification
ExpiryNotification : exit / Return to Service center home page --> ServiceCenterHome

ServiceCenterHome : exit / Updating Information list --> Updating parts Information
UpdatingPartsInformation : exit / Return to Service center home page --> ServiceCenterHome

ServiceCenterLogin : entry / Service Center not logged in --> ServiceCenterLogin
ServiceCenterLogin : do / Authenticate Service Center --> ServiceCenterLogin : exit / Logged In Successfully

ServiceCenterLogin : entry / Service Center already logged in --> ServiceCenterHome

ServiceCenterHome : exit / Logout --> Logout
Logout : exit / Logged out Successfully --> [*]

CarOwnerRegistration : entry / Unregistered Car Owner --> [*]
CarOwnerRegistration : do / Enter valid Credentials --> CarOwnerVerification
CarOwnerVerification : exit / Login Car Owner --> CarOwnerLogin

CarOwnerLogin : entry / Car owner not logged in --> CarOwnerLogin
CarOwnerLogin : do / Authenticate Car Owner --> CarOwnerLogin : exit / Logged In Successfully

CarOwnerHome : entry / Logged in Car Owner --> CarOwnerHome
CarOwnerHome : do / Display home page --> CarOwnerHome : exit / View parts information
CarOwnerHome : exit / Service --> Service
CarOwnerHome : exit / Report --> Report

Report : entry / To Report Service center --> Report : do / Enter the report --> CarOwnerHome : exit / Return to car owner home page

ViewPartsInformation : entry / To view parts information --> ViewPartsInformation : do / View car parts Information --> CarOwnerHome : exit / Return to Car owner home page

Service : entry / Service request from service center --> Service : do / Accept or deny request --> CarOwnerHome : exit / Return to Car Owner home page

ChooseParts : entry / To choose selected parts --> ChooseParts : do / Choose the part to be serviced --> Service : exit / Return to Service page

MakePayment : entry / To make payments --> MakePayment : do / Make payments --> Service : exit / Return to Service page
@enduml
